'''雨果·巴拉'''（{{lang-pt|Hugo Barra}}，1976年10月28日─），汉语人称'''虎哥'''，出生於[[巴西|巴西]][[贝洛奥里藏特|贝洛奥里藏特]]<ref name="epoca">{{cite web|url=http://revistaepoca.globo.com/vida/noticia/2011/10/o-brasileiro-que-manda-no-android.html|title=The Brazilian who runs Android|work=Época|access-date=2015-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141013164223/http://revistaepoca.globo.com/vida/noticia/2011/10/o-brasileiro-que-manda-no-android.html|archive-date=2014-10-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，是巴西{{cn|[[计算机|计算机]][[科学家|科学家]]}}、技术主管和[[企业家|企业家]]。他目前担任[[Facebook|Facebook]][[虛擬現實|虛擬現實]]業務的副总裁，负责[[Oculus_VR|Oculus VR]]团队和虚拟现实业务。<ref>[http://www.theverge.com/2017/1/25/14395062/hugo-barra-left-xiaomi-to-run-vr-at-facebook-oculus Hugo Barra left Xiaomi to run VR at Facebook].TheVerge.2016-01-26.[2016-01-26].</ref>

==生平==
1976年出生在巴西。从2008年到2013年，他在[[英國|英國]][[伦敦|伦敦]]和[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的[[谷歌|谷歌]]担任多个产品管理角色，其中包括副总裁，谷歌的[[Android|Android]]部门的产品代言人。<ref name="businessinsider.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/what-the-chinese-tech-industry-is-like-2014-1|title=This Famous Google Exec Quit His Job To Work In China — And He's Been Totally Blown Away By What He Found|work=Business Insider}}</ref>在2013年9月，巴拉从谷歌辞职来到小米科技公司，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allthingsd.com/20130912/exclusive-hugo-barra-talks-about-his-future-at-xiaomi-and-why-he-left-google/|title=Exclusive: Hugo Barra Talks About His Future at Xiaomi and Why He Really Left Google|work=All Things D}}</ref>他于2013年到2017年在[[中國|中國]][[小米科技|小米科技]]担任全球副总裁<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stuff.tv/android/hugo-barra-what-xiaomi-and-google-could-learn-each-other/feature|title=Hugo Barra on what Xiaomi and Google could learn from each other|work=Stuff}}</ref>。他曾参加LeWeb技术会议，并在LeWeb技术会议谈到了中国的经济留给他的印象以及中国科技代表之一的小米公司<ref>{{cite web|url=http://qz.com/156977/everything-you-need-to-know-about-chinese-tech-in-one-30-minute-video/|title=Everything you need to know about Chinese tech in one 30-minute video|work=Quartz.com}}</ref>。2017年1月23日，他宣布因为健康原因将离开小米科技，未来将会回到美国硅谷。<ref>[https://techcrunch.com/2017/01/22/hugo-barra-is-leaving-his-position-as-head-of-international-at-xiaomi-after-3-5-years/ Hugo Barra is leaving his position as head of international at Xiaomi after 3.5 years].TechCrunch.2017-01-23.[2017-01-23].</ref>外界分析稱，因北京持續的重度[[霧霾|霧霾]]導致他離開小米科技<ref>{{cite web|title=小米副總因「不可描述天氣現象」請辭？網笑小米高招|url=https://udn.com/news/story/7333/2254396|website=联合新闻网|accessdate=2017-01-28|date=2017-01-26}}</ref>。同月，他宣布加入[[Facebook|Facebook]]，担任虚拟现实业务的副总裁。

== 荣誉和奖励 ==
2011年，巴拉是在《[[连线|连线]]》（Wired）杂志的连线100名人榜排名第23名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2011/06/the-wired-100/the-wired-100-29-11|title=2nd annual Wired 100|work=Wired.co.uk}}</ref>在2013年，《[[商业内幕|商业内幕]]》杂志的[[硅谷|硅谷]]100名人榜包括巴拉在第92名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/the-silicon-valley-100-2013-2?op=1|title=The 100 Biggest Stars In Silicon Valley|work=Business Insider}}</ref>巴西{{le|EPOCA杂志|Época (Brazilian magazine)}}100名人榜最有影响力的巴西人排名巴拉是其中之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://revistaepoca.globo.com/vida/noticia/2011/12/epoca-100-os-brasileiros-mais-influentes-de-2011-trecho.html|title=Época Magazine: the 100 most influential Brazilians in 2011|work=Época Magazine|access-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216182124/http://revistaepoca.globo.com/vida/noticia/2011/12/epoca-100-os-brasileiros-mais-influentes-de-2011-trecho.html|archive-date=2017-02-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，评于2011年和2013年。

